) {\n            this.delegate.setErrorListener(listener);\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public ErrorListener getErrorListener() {\n            return this.delegate.getErrorListener();\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1132, "output": 1554, "cacheRead": 25088, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 27774, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1779496912440, "responseId": "resp_09d087b96f342ed4016a10f7d0df3c8197876e0e93b4e4fddf"}}
